ruby.text: def profile_allocations(name) GC.disable initial_size = ObjectSpace.count_objects yield changes = ObjectSpace.count_objects changes.each do |k, _| changes[k] -= initial_size[k] end puts '#{name} changes' changes.sort{|a,b| b[1] <=> a[1]}.each do |a,b| next if b <= 0 # 1 extra hash for trackingputs '#{a} #{a == :T_HASH ? b-1 : b}' end GC.enable end
